name: Abrasive/Grinding/Polish
description: This category hosts all products related to sanding, polishing and grinding. Whether you are looking for a backing pad, flap discs or polishing buffs, you will find it all here. This include wire brushes, sanding blocks, grinding points for die grinders, and all forms of abrasive sheets and rolls.
